    "body": "## Problem:\r\n`neovim` will spawn separate language server clients for files in `GOMODCACHE` and `GOROOT/src` directories if user goes there through `go to definition`.\r\n\r\n## Solution:\r\nUse already implemented solution from [gopls config](https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/blob/master/lsp/gopls.lua)",
